      "bbox": [
        119.88,
        57.65,
        312.07,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0005",
      "text": "4.3.1",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        118.22,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0006",
      "text": "Overview",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        82.97,
        172.62,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0007",
      "text": "An ELS Reply Sequence shall signify that the ELS request Sequence is completed.  The reply Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        540.07,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0008",
      "text": "quence may contain data in the Payload following the ELS_Command code word.  The format and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        118.97,
        540.0,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0009",
      "text": "meaning of the Payload is specified in the request ELS definition.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        383.74,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0010",
      "text": "4.3.2",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        118.23,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0011",
      "text": "LS_ACC",
      "bbox": [
        128.23,
        154.96,
        168.16,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0012",
      "text": "The Link Service Accept (LS_ACC) ELS reply Sequence shall notify the originator of an ELS request",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        540.01,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0013",
      "text": "that the ELS request Sequence has been completed.  The Responder shall terminate the Exchange",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        540.0,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0014",
      "text": "by setting the Last Sequence bit (Bit 20) in F_CTL on the last Data frame of the reply Sequence.  The",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        540.04,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0015",
      "text": "first byte of the Payload shall contain 02h.  The remainder of the Payload is unique to the ELS re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        540.0,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0016",
      "text": "quest.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        123.17,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0017",
      "text": "Protocol: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        142.66,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0018",
      "text": "LS_ACC is the reply Sequence for several ELSs as indicated in the applicable clause.",
      "bbox": [
        142.62,
        250.96,
        522.0,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0019",
      "text": "Addressing: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        157.1,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0020",
      "text": "The D_ID field designates the source of the ELS Sequence being accepted while the",
      "bbox": [
        157.08,
        274.96,
        539.96,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0021",
      "text": "S_ID field designates the destination of the request Sequence being accepted.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        443.21,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0022",
      "text": "Payload: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        140.41,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0023",
      "text": "The Payload content following the ELS_Command code (02XXXXXXh) is defined within in-",
      "bbox": [
        140.4,
        310.96,
        540.08,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0024",
      "text": "dividual ELS requests.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        195.39,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0025",
      "text": "4.3.3",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        118.22,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0026",
      "text": "Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        128.22,
        346.96,
        205.41,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
