        118.24,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0029",
      "text": "Link Service Reject (LS_RJT)",
      "bbox": [
        128.25,
        394.96,
        266.52,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0030",
      "text": "4.3.4.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        187.03,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0031",
      "text": "The Link Service Reject (LS_RJT) shall notify the transmitter of a Link Service request that the Link",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        539.99,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0032",
      "text": "Service request Sequence has been rejected.  A four-byte reason code shall be contained in the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        539.9,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0033",
      "text": "Data Field.  Link Service Reject may be transmitted for a variety of conditions that may be unique to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        540.02,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0034",
      "text": "a specific Link Service request (e.g., if the Service Parameters specified in a Login frame were logi-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        540.01,
        490.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0035",
      "text": "cally inconsistent or in error, a P_RJT frame would not be transmitted in response, but rather a Link",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        540.02,
        502.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0036",
      "text": "Service Reject).",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        166.47,
        514.07
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0037",
      "text": "4.3.4.2  Payload",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        170.43,
        538.07
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0038",
      "text": "Addressing: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        157.1,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0039",
      "text": "The D_ID field designates the source of the ELS request being rejected while the S_ID",
      "bbox": [
        157.08,
        550.96,
        539.96,
        562.07
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0040",
      "text": "field designates the destination of the request Data frame Sequence being rejected.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        465.41,
        574.07
      ],
      "block_index": 17,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0041",
      "text": "Payload: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        140.41,
        598.07
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0042",
      "text": "The first word of the Payload shall contain the ELS_Command code (01000000h).  The",
      "bbox": [
        140.4,
        586.96,
        539.92,
        598.07
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0043",
      "text": "next four bytes of this field shall indicate the reason for rejecting the request (see figure 3 and tables",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        540.01,
        610.07
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0044",
      "text": "146 and 147).  The first error condition encountered shall be the error reported.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        444.9,
        622.07
      ],
      "block_index": 18,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0045",
      "text": "NOTE 8 – The applicable ELSs column in table 147 is not necessarily complete  (i.e., a given reply may con-",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        635.17,
        539.87,
        645.22
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p146_s0046",
      "text": "tain a reason code explanation other than what is indicated for it in the table).",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        646.22,
        411.25,
        656.26
      ],
      "block_index": 19,
